TextEng: What is causing the rage?
Why did you attack me?
What cause rage?
Why you attack me?
What could affect your mind in such a strong manner?
Text: 무엇이 당신 마음을 그렇게 강하게 영향을 줄 수 있죠?

TextEng: It seems to be affecting the whole forest.
Text: 숲 전체에 영향을 미치는 것 같아요.

TextEng: What control you mind?
Whole forest go crazy!
Do you know what I might do to stop it?
Stay calm and keep control. I don't want to have to hurt you anymore.
Text: 침착하고 통제를 유지하세요. 더 이상 당신을 다치게 하고 싶지 않아요.

TextEng: I think I had better kill you before you try to kill me.
Text: 당신이 날 죽이기 전에 죽이는 게 나을 것 같아요.

TextEng: What me do to stop it?
You be calm so me no have to hurt you no more.
Text: 너 침착해야 돼, 그래야 나 더 안 다치게 해.

TextEng: Me no trust you. Me must kill you now.
Text: 나 너 믿지 않아. 나 지금 너 죽여야 돼.

TextEng: I guess you had better flee now. Goodbye.
Text: 이제 도망치는 게 좋을 것 같네요. 안녕.

TextEng: You run away now. Goodbye.
Who wouldn't be affected?
Who no be affected?
Tell me about the druids.
Why would the nymphs not be affected?
Tell me more about the witch.
What druids you mean?
Why nymphs be not crazy?
Which witch?
What do you mean 'because of her face?'
I think your madness is getting worse.
What you meaning her face?
You getting more crazy?
I'm not going to hurt you, now stop yelling at me.
Text: 당신을 다치게 하지 않을 거예요, 이제 소리 지르지 마세요.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You can trust me dear. Why don't you tell me what you know?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 날 믿어도 돼요. 아는 걸 말해 주지 않을래요?

TextEng: Me not hurt you, but you stop yelling.
Text: 나 너 안 다치게 해, 근데 너 소리 지르지 마.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me no hurt you. Me you friend. You tell me what you know.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 너 안 다치게 해. 나 너 친구야. 너 아는 거 말해줘.

TextEng: You tell me, or I'll chop your tree into kindling!
Text: 말해, 아니면 네 나무를 불쏘시개로 만들어버릴 거야!

TextEng: You tell me, or me chop tree and make big fire!
Text: 말해, 아니면 나 나무 잘라서 큰 불 만들어!
